spec_data.Name: python-tw-forms
spec_data.Description:
tw.forms is a set of html and javascript widgets for the ToscaWidgets
framework.  They give authors basic html form elements as building blocks
for their own web pages and widgets.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 04:53:43 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Web Widgets for building and validating forms in ToscaWidgets
